query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `health_alerts` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `enabled` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `alertChannelId` VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  `offlineAlertEnabled` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `errorAlertEnabled` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `errorThreshold` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 5,
  `checkIntervalSeconds` INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 60,
  `lastHealthCheck` TIMESTAMP NULL,
  `createdAt` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
